{"tid":1234102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚閪咩]咪同佢鬥坐 唔速戰速決 你和平讓路同佢拖","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T00:57:44.000Z","uid":4746,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d292b6cbbf48777510ed0bf07decb28b5f267ae","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:40.000Z","msg":"佢消民意咪速戰速決 你和平 佢理閪得理 69和平抗爭唔係未試過啦<br />\n一班人出黎話唔好衝 邊撚個有衝呀<br />\n你唔坐係度抗爭 你返行人路坐有閪用 你返行人路坐 你返屋企啦 唔俾更多壓力政府 <br />\n你返行人路坐 到時人多個陣邊個衝出馬路佔 又俾人衝一個拉一個呀?<br />\n本身佔緊既 驚閪咩 出談判專家 你唔係受硬 今次受軟呀?<br />\n香港人係善忘既 呢啲係人性 你呢幾日唔迫政府 你玩得幾多日? 仲有人叫返入行人路 ?<br />\n<br />\n黑警所做既一切 無論軟又好 硬又好 都唔應該受 <br />\n佢玩軟攻 你就受 你唔係中計咁係咩<br />\n話玩伏 呢段時間市民都嬲到子彈都唔驚 你唔係等佢平息左 再同你傾呀? <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你睇下政府態度係咩先啦 佢做咩都當你臭四 你唔做返啲野俾人睇 係度哂時間俾佢地休息?</span></span>"},{"pid":"15064e6e0a8bdde7a41636ed6b37be90bacea2cd","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:41:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你殺佢操手不及 反而俾時間佢地諗之後點應對<br />\n好多人都話要衝先出返黎 唔做野 邊有人再出返黎</span></span>"},{"pid":"53025f4255a8e05c4315166e081cb5b93958fcc1","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又俾人拖拖就算 可能香港真係死左<br />\n大家一齊放棄啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"3960f88d74f2bf8e7c0eeb09c35346316403e3bb","tid":1234102,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無人幫手整poster /長輩圖方便文宣！！！唔可以輕易俾香港人忘記！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 未撤回&quot;送中/逃犯條例&quot;<br />\n2. 未切查警察濫用武力、濫權、濫捕<br />\n3. 612 依然被定性為&quot;暴動&quot;, 想秋後算帳示威者<br />\n4. 未釋放被捕示威者<br />\n5. 林鄭未下台"},{"pid":"2b286ec67808763955cbdfbb1c604e6efa1f4c43","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:48:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有優勢唔去繼續 唔去俾人睇 無人會理之後會點架啦 越黎越多事 又問責黑驚 又放人 由始至終都係想撤回<br />\n今次唔繼續留守 仲可以有咩做</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f31d3a34a890832e2c2ed4136486445274fc8be","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又再等人過黎 不如自己做返野啦 你唔係信唔做野 會有人黎呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"29584e755dc7dfcdf776a50f3adb063426447970","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤回 不撤退去左邊?</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f578cd188302e453b38d6bd892009eef9349aee","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次讓步真係輸哂個優勢</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd23454758d29d451c942918bafb070e2bd82f53","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:52:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又有人玩分化 收錢做野個啲仲熱心過真正愛港既香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a9a6acf40cfe976058e3f27b12c71b4239889b2","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:53:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禮咩賓府 一路矛頭指向立法會 咁都俾人講到轉軚 香港玩完佢算啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"55fb3bca6a6c64a8bcef1a3a0467cdb428c06507","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人會理 無事發生既野 </span></span>"},{"pid":"90c77922563e063d901931e55f633cf66fabfd9d","tid":1234102,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家各有各做 人咪散鳩